%% One chat turn from user message to chat_complete frame
%% Render: mmdc -i agentic-loop-sequence.mmd -o agentic-loop-sequence.svg

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User / WS
    participant C as ChatService
    participant L as LLMProvider.chat()
    participant T as Tool registry
    participant A as UIMutationsAccumulator

    U->>C: chat_message
    Note over C: persist user msg, build prompt, load tools

    rect rgb(238,242,255)
        Note right of C: Iteration 1
        C->>L: chat(history, tools, system_prompt)
        L-->>C: tool_calls=[search_candidates, set_highlights]
        C->>T: execute(search_candidates, ...)
        T-->>C: { matches, ... }
        C->>U: tool_status (executing → complete)
        C->>T: execute(set_highlights, ...)
        T-->>C: { ui_state, mutation }
        C->>U: tool_status (executing → complete)
        C->>A: merge(mutation)
    end

    rect rgb(238,242,255)
        Note right of C: Iteration 2
        C->>L: chat(history += tool_results)
        L-->>C: text="Highlighted 5 senior engineers", no tool_calls
    end

    Note over C: persist assistant msg + accumulated ui_mutations
    C-->>U: chat_complete { text, ui_mutations, iterations, truncated }

    Note over C,U: If iteration == MAX_ITERATIONS (5) and<br/>the model still wants to call tools,<br/>we break with truncated=true.
